  "source_text": "When Kroxa enters, sacrifice it unless it escaped.\nWhenever Kroxa enters or attacks, each opponent discards a card, then each opponent who didn't discard a nonland card this way loses 3 life.\nEscape—{B}{B}{R}{R}, Exile five other cards from your graveyard. (You may cast this card from your graveyard for its escape cost.)",
  "card_name": "Kroxa, Titan of Death's Hunger"
